data.description: Welcome to your dream POOL home in Las Vegas! This stunning 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom single story home offers the perfect blend of modern upgrades + comfortable living. As you step inside, you are greeted by a spacious & inviting floorpan that seamlessly flows to the backyard oasis: pristinely maintained pool, NEW lush turf and covered patio with fan. Front and rear living spaces are connected by the heart of the home: the kitchen, boasting sleek quartz countertops, contemporary cabinetry, farmhouse sink & breakfast bar. Custom pantry & dry bar add ample storage space. Neutral color palette & abundant natural light give the home a bright & airy ambiance. Step inside the primary bedroom with walk-in closet, spa-like tiled bathroom + double vanity. NEW pool vac + child/pet safe pool cover. Tesla solar panels @ $54/M. TIMELESS UPGRADES THROUGHOUT. Water softener, reverse osmosis + water purification system, new water heater & pressure regulator! All warranties transferred to buyer. Must see!
